{"tid":1325743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(721沉完又開) 你哋唔記得啦？你應承過我嫁","createTime":"2019-07-17T03:35:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T04:18:12.000Z","uid":181257,"like":219,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":86,"replies":[{"pid":"c5a5b63d82a3e0b0d950bb7f76afe891078ad7d1","tid":1325743,"uid":181257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T03:35:04.000Z","msg":"還記得我們對他許下的諾言嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oPaUq3D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoPaUq3D.png&h=e21e3fcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Ektvvn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Ektvvn.png&h=0d40a0d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n已經一個多月了，五大訴求有無一項做到？<br />\n一百萬人上街 政府唔理<br />\n二百萬人上街 政府唔理<br />\n有人以死明志 政府唔理<br />\n警察受輕傷 政府仆到去理<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我唔知再出最後結果係咪都一樣，但係，我哋應承得嘅，就一定要做，一日未達成共識，都要出<br />\n<br />\n大家成年人 唔洗再睇風向做人 要點做自己諗<br />\n<br />\n但我想問一個問題，咁多人犧牲 受傷 被補<br />\n如果結果係咁 你甘心咩？"},{"pid":"11d96e6f65986d494bb965fb6d82cf331f37323d","tid":1325743,"uid":3981,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T03:37:53.000Z","msg":"香港人 加油"},{"pid":"043d774160c76fda8ca72030e9cd64b1540898b4","tid":1325743,"uid":162327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T03:38:45.000Z","msg":"有冇721詳情 完全搵唔到集中post"},{"pid":"587eceecb0b567046755c0fc965324de9521b493","tid":1325743,"uid":181257,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T03:42:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d16e80da9dea2e2fad199550dbc4219154d4e330","tid":1325743,"uid":181257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T03:42:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ac1ddadd878fa7ce535e611fbcc674b7507cf36","tid":1325743,"uid":273991,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3