/span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">唔理衝唔衝21去金鐘</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">我無嘢講 我要見律師 我要驗傷 我唔解鎖電話 我唔簽任何文件\n\n5大訴求：\n1. 立即撤回送中條例\n2. 除消暴動定義\n3. 不再追究義士\n4. 成立獨立調查\n5. 真雙普選</code></pre>"},{"pid":"7bea6ab88fc97c66a780df7803ec0a94a45e0d1b","tid":1325743,"uid":181257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:36:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/isx34fi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fisx34fi.png&h=1f9d670e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b7556f53a3cd2f403404d2459f2b92fa02125dcf","tid":1325743,"uid":181257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:37:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82fdb53d57d86f9130c404a490fc1b4c774bffdb","tid":1325743,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"043d774160c76fda8ca72030e9cd64b1540898b4","tid":1325743,"uid":162327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T03:38:45.000Z","msg":"有冇721詳情 完全搵唔到集中post"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:40:10.000Z","msg":"Not yet confirmed"},{"pid":"522d45b323e3d1a465e15e6b750d0247e1eba20c","tid":1325743,"uid":216685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:49:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b0134d93a953b62c57d03fc116b1203e357ce00","tid":1325743,"uid":21108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:51:39.000Z","msg":"721情報新嘗試!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1325201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1325201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n幫手推呀 就黎沉喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d15d720c015f8bcc1f78f66043065aabf3c5058","tid":1325743,"uid":38482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:52:23.000Z","msg":"熱門冇哂野餐po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif