 style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">721! HONGKONGERS! ASSEMBLE!</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1327503/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1327503/page/1</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1326334/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1326334/page/1</a></span>"},{"pid":"5dd8aaf931495703c72a3d460d00a8f82e0126dd","tid":1325743,"uid":268692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5a5b63d82a3e0b0d950bb7f76afe891078ad7d1","tid":1325743,"uid":181257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T03:35:04.000Z","msg":"還記得我們對他許下的諾言嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oPaUq3D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoPaUq3D.png&h=e21e3fcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Ektvvn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Ektvvn.png&h=0d40a0d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n已經一個多月了，五大訴求有無一項做到？<br />\n一百萬人上街 政府唔理<br />\n二百萬人上街 政府唔理<br />\n有人以死明志 政府唔理<br />\n警察受輕傷 政府仆到去理<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我唔知再出最後結果係咪都一樣，但係，我哋應承得嘅，就一定要做，一日未達成共識，都要出<br />\n<br />\n大家成年人 唔洗再睇風向做人 要點做自己諗<br />\n<br />\n但我想問一個問題，咁多人犧牲 受傷 被補<br />\n如果結果係咁 你甘心咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T08:07:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1.）撤回逃犯修例<br />\n2.）撤回暴動定性<br />\n3.）無條件釋放被捕示威者<br />\n4.）追究警方暴力濫權<br />\n5.）香港要雙普選<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山 各有各做<br />\n多你一個好多<br />\n約定身邊啲親朋戚友<br />\n<br />\n721去維園!!<br />\n721去維園!!<br />\n721去維園!!<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 重奪自由<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"882a7acda8d592a531592160e7f5f4e1423b1e36","tid":1325743,"uid":263221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T08:07:36.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"c9bb4a408a605084f527fd309d0aa01f2ff240b4","tid":1325743,"uid":181257,"like":0,"dislike":